<span class="nt">-------------------</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span>git status
<span class="c"># иҫ“еҮә</span>
On branch dev
nothing to commit, working directory clean  <span class="c"># е№ІеҮҖеҫ—еҫҲ</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҒҡе…¶е®ғд»»еҠЎ">еҒҡе…¶е®ғд»»еҠЎ
  <a href="/tutorials/others/git/4-4-stash/#еҒҡе…¶е®ғд»»еҠЎ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>з„¶еҗҺжҲ‘д»¬е»әз«ӢеҸҰдёҖдёӘ <code class="highlighter-rouge">branch</code> з”ЁжқҘе®ҢжҲҗиҖҒжқҝзҡ„д»»еҠЎ:</p>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>git checkout <span class="nt">-b</span> boss

<span class="c"># иҫ“еҮә</span>
Switched to a new branch <span class="s1">'boss'</span> <span class="c"># еҲӣе»әе№¶еҲҮжҚўеҲ° boss</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>з„¶еҗҺиӢҰйҖјең°е®ҢжҲҗзқҖиҖҒжқҝзҡ„д»»еҠЎ, жҜ”еҰӮж·»еҠ  <code class="highlighter-rouge"># lovely boss</code> еҺ» <code class="highlighter-rouge">1.py</code>. з„¶еҗҺ <code class="highlighter-rouge">commit</code>, е®ҢжҲҗиҖҒжқҝзҡ„д»»еҠЎ.</p>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>git commit <span class="nt">-am</span> <span class="s2">"job from boss"</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span>git checkout master
<span class="nv">$ </span>git merge <span class="nt">--no-ff</span> <span class="nt">-m</span> <span class="s2">"merged boss job"</span> boss
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">merge</code> еҰӮжһңжңүеҶІзӘҒзҡ„иҜқ, еҸҜд»ҘеғҸ<a href="/tutorials/others/git/4-2-merge-conflict/">дёҠж¬ЎйӮЈж ·</a>
и§ЈеҶі.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="c1"># I went back to change 1
</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="n">HEAD</span>

<span class="c1"># edited in master and dev
</span>
<span class="o">=======</span>
<span class="c1"># edited in dev
</span>
<span class="c1"># lovely boss
